# Badge 徽标

用于展示计数或状态提示。

## 基础用法
::TuffDemo{title="徽标样式" description="数量、文本与点状提示。" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxBadge :value="8" />
    <TxBadge value="New" variant="primary" />
    <TxBadge value="99+" variant="success" />
    <TxBadge dot variant="error" />
  </template>
---
#preview
<div class="tuff-demo-row">
  <tx-badge :value="8" />
  <tx-badge value="New" variant="primary" />
  <tx-badge value="99+" variant="success" />
  <tx-badge dot variant="error" />
</div>
:::

## API（Lite）
::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: variant
    type: "'default' | 'primary' | 'success' | 'warning' | 'error'"
    default: "'default'"
    description: 颜色类型
  - name: value
    type: "string | number"
    default: '0'
    description: 徽标内容
  - name: dot
    type: boolean
    default: 'false'
    description: 点状模式
  - name: color
    type: string
    default: '-'
    description: 自定义颜色
---
:::

